node.text: Wow how cool are these?! Love everything matcha 💚🍵

🥐Burnt Matcha Cheese Cruffins from @keongsaikbakery made my day really! Love that the Matcha filling was gao enough! The best way of eating this was to toast it in the oven for a few mins till crispy and the filling is flowy 🥰 ⁣
⁣
Pickup and islandwide delivery is available for their pastries. Check out their ig @keongsaikbakery for more deets 😘 Happy week guys!⁣
